      "The EAWR is a Statutory Regulation, meaning it is the law that sets the mandatory legal duty for safety.",
      "BS 7671 is a Non-statutory Regulation, which acts as the technical guidance or standard used to prove that the legal requirements of the EAWR have been met."
    ],
    "hint": "Think about which one tells you 'you must be safe' (the law) and which one tells you 'how to be safe' (the technical standard)."
  }
}

